    <ul id="cRzMN6L7hzulcPt-dOovn">
      <li id="6w">
        <p>Dear Dahee</p>
        <ul>
          <li id="n_D">
            <p>I am so sorry I hurt you and I made you cry. This was never my intention. However, nothing can excuse my actions. I was shocked by my own behaviour and how careless I was, and I regret everything. Travelling with you and camping with you has made such a special memory that I will cherish for so many years. I really want to have more adventures with you. I love you so much and I am so sorry. Please forgive me and the hurt I caused you. I never meant for this to happen and I am so upset with myself that I allowed myself to bring pain to you. I love you.</p>
          </li>
          <li id="nXw6">
            <p/>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li id="7Ax">
        <p>First Person Singular </p>
        <ul>
          <li id="uz8">
            <p>I am particularly fond of this extract, from the first chapter, which</p>
          </li>
          <li id="UN">
            <p>is aptly titled "Cream":</p>
          </li>
          <li id="c_">
            <p/>
          </li>
          <li id="83w">
            <p>&gt; "There's nothing worth getting in this world that you can get easily."</p>
          </li>
          <li id="Rr">
            <p>&gt; Then, as if starting a new paragraph, he briefly cleared his</p>
          </li>
          <li id="ru">
            <p>&gt; throat. "But, when you put in that much time and effort, if you do</p>
          </li>
          <li id="Ar">
            <p>&gt; achieve that difficult thing it becomes the cream of your life."</p>
          </li>
          <li id="Xsx">
            <p>&gt;   "Cream?"</p>
          </li>
          <li id="rH">
            <p>&gt;   "In French, they have an expression: creme de la creme.</p>
          </li>
          <li id="QSA">
            <p>&gt; Do you know it?"</p>
          </li>
          <li id="ep">
            <p>&gt;</p>
          </li>
          <li id="SM">
            <p>&gt;   "I don't." I said. I knew no French.</p>
          </li>
          <li id="JH">
            <p>&gt;   "The cream of the cream. It means the best of the best.</p>
          </li>
          <li id="jr">
            <p>&gt; The most important essence of life&amp;#x2013;that's the creme de la creme.</p>
          </li>
          <li id="_N">
            <p>&gt; Get it? The rest is just boring and worthless."</p>
          </li>
          <li id="NE">
            <p>&gt; Murakami</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li id="KJT9">
        <p/>
      </li>
      <li id="GGwZ">
